    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been loved and well-taken care of? This beauty is in great shape and ready for its next adventure with you! It runs like a dream and looks fantastic parked in the driveway. I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, so it\u2019s totally road-trip ready. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
