      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is equipped with a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. To address common platform weaknesses, the rod bearings have been replaced and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates. The double VANOS system is quiet and responsive, ensuring the individual throttle bodies provide immediate throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup that maintains excellent lateral grip. While the aesthetics show honest wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a refreshed cooling system and consistent compression across all six cylinders.",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior. Mechanically sound. Clean title in hand.",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2019 Executive Sport Sedan that strikes the perfect balance between spirited performance and refined comfort. The exterior is finished in a deep Metallic Charcoal that retains a brilliant depth and luster; while you may find a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel consistent with careful daily use, the body panels are remarkably straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of premium black leather and brushed aluminum. The upholstery remains supple and clean, showing only light softening on the driver's side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the advanced driver-assistance suite and the premium 12-speaker audio system, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been pampered. It comes with a complete service log showing oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent major 60,000-mile service that included new spark plugs and a cooling system flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brake pads were replaced just last season. On the road, the engine pulls smoothly with its original vigor, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. This is a reliable, turn-key enthusiast's car for someone who appreciates a vehicle that has been genuinely cared for.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sophisticated styling. This unit has been meticulously maintained to ensure consistent performance and driver comfort. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it offers a premier driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to inspect this exceptional offering, which stands as a testament to quality engineering and responsible ownership.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
