      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super dependable for all my daily errands and the occasional road trip. It drives smoothly, looks sharp, and has definitely been well-loved and taken care of. If you're looking for a solid, reliable car that's ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is powered by the M96 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, providing a linear power band and an unmistakable boxer howl. The 6-speed G96 manual transaxle offers precise gate engagement, complemented by a chassis that remains composed through high-load cornering. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the communicative hydraulic steering feel and rear-engine traction dynamics that define the 911 lineage. A mechanically sorted example ready for spirited driving.",
